  "description": "<i>Blades of Vengeance</i> is a platform game incorporating light RPG elements and character styling, reminiscent of <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/gods\">Gods</a> by <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?company=Bitmap+Brothers\">The Bitmap Brothers</a>. The Dark Lady has unleashed hordes of monsters whom the protagonist must slay.<br><br>The player can choose from three main characters - the Huntress, Warrior and Sorcerer, all of which have different abilities. Throughout the game the player has the option to improve their powers by collecting armour and weapons (such as a mace and a crossbow) or by using spells. Each of the eight stages ends with a boss.",
